character.name: Isometric pixel art character of a middle-aged male executive, around 45–50 years old, wealthy and elegant in appearance but not flashy. He wears a perfectly tailored charcoal gray suit with a light blue dress shirt and a subtle silk tie. His hair is slicked back neatly with a few gray strands, and he has a clean-shaven face with sharp features. Expression shows anger and disappointment, eyebrows furrowed, lips pressed tight, eyes narrowed as if reprimanding an employee for losing a million-dollar contract. Stands with tense posture, one hand on his hip and the other pointing slightly forward as if in frustration. The overall color tone is balanced and professional, evoking authority and control. Transparent background, clean edges, consistent with 2D isometric RPG game style.
